{"thag2.49:0.1":"Theragatha 2.49 ","thag2.49:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.49:0.3":"Pancamavagga ","thag2.49:0.4":"Sandhitattheragatha ","thag2.49:1.1":"“Assatthe haritobhase, ","thag2.49:1.2":"samvirulhamhi padape; ","thag2.49:1.3":"Ekam buddhagatam sannam, ","thag2.49:1.4":"alabhittham patissato. ","thag2.49:2.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","thag2.49:2.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","thag2.49:2.3":"Tassa sannaya vahasa, ","thag2.49:2.4":"patto me asavakkhayo”ti. ","thag2.49:2.5":"… Sandhito thero … ","thag2.49:2.6":"vaggo pancamo. ","thag2.49:3.0":"Tassuddanam ","thag2.49:3.1":"Kumarakassapo thero, ","thag2.49:3.2":"dhammapalo ca brahmali; ","thag2.49:3.3":"Mogharaja visakho ca, ","thag2.49:3.4":"culako ca anupamo; ","thag2.49:3.5":"Vajjito sandhito thero, ","thag2.49:3.6":"kilesarajavahanoti. ","thag2.49:3.7":"Dukanipato nitthito. ","thag2.49:4.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag2.49:4.1":"Gathadukanipatamhi, ","thag2.49:4.2":"navuti ceva attha ca; ","thag2.49:4.3":"Thera ekunapannasam, ","thag2.49:4.4":"bhasita nayakovidati. "}